{"tid":1093753,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日回憶舊時","createTime":"2019-04-05T20:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T20:29:59.000Z","uid":5968,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3644fd6a6a824ea4666060b717569d731057582f","tid":1093753,"uid":5968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T20:01:51.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲人，明明係最應該向前望<br />\n但係就唔知點鍾意諗起以前<br />\n<br />\n細個覺得聽舊歌真係好老土<br />\n而家新歌聽唔入耳，開始係咁loop舊歌<br />\n<br />\n係咪一個人無寄托就會成日諗以前？<br />\n<br />\n一諗到自己活係過去就覺得自己好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e831d7b38297ae29bc618f38602f1802364114e","tid":1093753,"uid":119125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T20:03:15.000Z","msg":"我都成日懷愐過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6b07e34434eee3e1e75eb08acda5b3a755b9dd","tid":1093753,"uid":5968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T20:06:32.000Z","msg":"其實以前唔算特別好<br />\n又唔係有錢，又無乜娛樂<br />\n<br />\n但硬係覺得以前開心d"},{"pid":"5ea250c6b26efe4dc97b72352b411ee9231abe20","tid":1093753,"uid":90441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T20:10:43.000Z","msg":"因為以為開心過依加 所以咪成日回想之前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abb4d5aa9b6a8365a2fa42e71449897dabd9605","tid":1093753,"uid":5968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T20:15:30.000Z","msg":"又或者朋友兄弟開始有另一半<br />\n開始成家立室<br />\n<br />\n感覺上好似得番自己咁<br />\n又好似無形中有少少壓力<br />\n<br />\n個個都向前行緊<br />\n唯獨我一個望緊返轉頭"},{"pid":"9e1595e7b6430364eda891318e51ba301f9f25a3","tid":1093753,"uid":25369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T20:25:21.000Z","msg":"因為太多決定做錯/做得唔好，好多後悔，所以成日諗返以前<br />\n<br />\n但時間一秒一秒咁過，諗太多只會更後悔"},{"pid":"be2e9572452b62a2cbc99051339c717d98a4d106","tid":1093753,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T20:29:59.000Z","msg":"因為你唔滿意現況先會咁"}]}